song.title: Mirage
song.info:
Don't listen with hardware mixing (ie. AWE32 or GUS) if possible- you'll miss out on a LOT of notes. (both on reasons of pitch an number of notes)
If your computer can't handle the number of channels, lower the mixing rate (as opposed to limiting the channels). The channels are more important that high playback quality.
Channels used: 36 Virtual channels: 96
